getMainContents

protected abstract java.lang.Object getMainContents()
Get this unit of work's main contents.

The main contents distinguish this unit of work from another or match it to another. The main contents should not rely on status or reason.

recordFailure

public void recordFailure(java.lang.String reason)
Record the failure of this unit of work.

If the reason is null, assume that the unit of work failed because of a "false" return value while being processed in a job and set the work status to FAILED; otherwise, set the work status to ERROR and record the non-null reason.

Specified by:
recordFailure in interface UnitOfWork
Parameters:
reason - either null for 'normal' failure or a stack trace signalling error;
